Firstly this would be a calendar and day planner app

Currently the ideas for features include
Setting up calendar with clickable events
Daily to do list
Reminders with notifications
Dark mode / Light mode switch
Setup different lists of tasks
Setup a series of tasks e.g. one that happens every friday etc.
Smart Conflict Detection
Export to outlook
Assignment / Deadline Tracker & Exam Countdown
Widget for home screen
Tag search through the events for a particular day
Import from outlook
Export to Google Calendar
Import from Google Calendar
We will check if these count as features then add them to the Trello

Priority levels